{COUNCILLOR MR.MICHAEL WILLIAMS { COUNCILLOR MRS.WILLOW WILLIAMS}
Mr.& Mrs.Williams are my mum and dad.Mr.Williams has been a councillor for 18\ years.He represents Gwersyllt on the Wrexham Maelor District Council,and is a member of the Gwersyllt Community Council. In 1985 Mr.Williams was made leader of the Wrexham Maelor District Council.From 1978-1979 he was Mayor of Wrexham. Mrs.Williams has been a councillor for the past three years.She serves on the Gwersyllt Community Council. As councillors they are trying to make Gwersyllt a better place to live in.
{Robert Williams aged 10
